uth-350px.jpg|75px]] | [[Saguenay River|Saguenay Fjord]] | [[Laurentian Highlands]] | Quebec | 7,590 |- | | [[Saugeen Shores, Ontario|Saugeen Shores]] sunsets | Saugeen Shores | Ontario | 7,493 |- | | [[Basin Head, Prince Edward Island|Singing Sands Beach]] | Basin Head | [[Prince Edward Island]] | 8,232 |- | [[File:Spiral Tunnels 1908 Kodak.jpg|75px]] | [[Big Hill#The Spiral Tunnels|Spiral Tunnels]] | [[Canadian Rockies]] | British Columbia | 8,755 |- | [[Image:Stanley cup closeup.jpg|75px]] | The [[Stanley Cup]] | | | 19,581 |- | [[Image:Trans-Canada-wildlife overpass.JPG|75px]] | [[Trans-Canada Highway]] | | | 14,753 |- | [[Image:Pingos near Tuk.jpg|75px]] | [[Pingo National Landmark|Tuktoyaktuk Pingos]] | [[Tuktoyaktuk, Northwest Territories|Tuktoyaktuk]] | Northwest Territories | 5,987 |- | [[Image:Pysanka.jpg|75px]] | [[Vegreville egg]] | [[Vegreville]] | Alberta | 5,444 |- | [[File:Vimy Memorial - Allward design submission.jpg|75px]] | [[Canadian National Vimy Memorial|Vimy Memorial]] | France | | 15,462 |- | [[Image:Wreckbeach-ptgrey.jpg|75px]] | [[Wreck Beach]] | [[Pacific Spirit Regional Park]] | British Columbia | 7,143 |}
